                    <span>Im a 15 year old student and  just finsished reading this book (and am writing a 10 page paper for in in A.P history  :( )This was an excellant book. Allen is very insightfull for his time. The changes that occur, and the analysis he gives are parallel to those of present day. The only dull point was the Harding Scandal, but otherwise the rest was a good read. I like his sense of humor. <p>Flip Side</span>
                  
              
